article_title: Health insurance premiums lower than seemed
article_text:
Health insurance premiums lower than seemed

A new report from the U.S. Department of Health and Human Services demonstrates that proposed premium changes from preliminary rate filings do not capture what Marketplace consumers actually pay.

Posted May. 16, 2016 at 8:06 AM
